Package sx.blah.discord.handle.impl.events

This package contains all the events that Discord4J supports.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllUsersReceivedEvent
    This event gets called on large servers which require members to be sent out over time.
    ChannelCreateEvent
    This event is dispatched when a channel is created.
    ChannelDeleteEvent
    This event is dispatched when a channel is deleted.
    ChannelUpdateEvent
    This event is dispatched when a channel's information is updated.
    DisconnectedEvent
    This event is dispatched when either a shard loses connection to discord or is logged out.
    DiscordDisconnectedEvent Deprecated
    Use DisconnectedEvent
    DiscordReconnectedEvent Deprecated
    Use ReconnectSuccessEvent
    GuildCreateEvent
    This event is dispatched when a guild is created/ the bot joins the guild.
    GuildEmojisUpdateEvent
    Fired whenever emojis change in a guild.
    GuildLeaveEvent
    This event is dispatched when a guild is deleted or the bot is kicked.
    GuildTransferOwnershipEvent
    This event is dispatched when a guild's ownership is transferred.
    GuildUnavailableEvent
    This event is dispatched when a guild becomes unavailable.
    GuildUpdateEvent
    This event is dispatched when a guild is edited by its owner.
    InviteReceivedEvent
    This event is dispatched when a message the bot receives includes an invite link.
    LoginEvent
    This event is fired when a shard has established an initial connection to the Discord gateway.
    MentionEvent
    This event is dispatched whenever the bot is @mentioned.
    MessageDeleteEvent
    This event is dispatched whenever a message is deleted.
    MessageEmbedEvent
    This event is dispatched whenever a message is edited.
    MessagePinEvent
    This event is fired when a message is pinned to a channel.
    MessageReceivedEvent
    This event is dispatched whenever a message is received.
    MessageSendEvent
    This event is dispatched whenever a message is sent by the bot.
    MessageUnpinEvent
    This event is fired when a message is unpinned from a channel.
    MessageUpdateEvent
    This event is dispatched whenever a message is edited.
    ModuleDisabledEvent
    This event is dispatched when a module is disabled.
    ModuleEnabledEvent
    This event is dispatched when a module is enabled.
    NickNameChangeEvent
    This is fired once a nickname is changed.
    PresenceUpdateEvent
    This event is dispatched when a user changes his/her presence.
    ReactionAddEvent
    Fired when a reaction gets added to a message.
    ReactionRemoveEvent
    Fired when a reaction gets removed from a message.
    ReadyEvent
    This event is dispatched when all shards are ready to interact with the api.
    ReconnectFailureEvent
    Fired when a reconnect attempt for a shard fails.
    ReconnectSuccessEvent
    Fired when a shard has succeeded in connecting to the gateway.
    ResumedEvent
    Fired when the client receives a RESUMED payload from the gateway.
    RoleCreateEvent
    This event is dispatched whenever a role is created.
    RoleDeleteEvent
    This event is dispatched after a role has been deleted from a guild.
    RoleUpdateEvent
    This event is dispatched whenever a guild role is modified.
    ShardReadyEvent
    This event is dispatched when a shard is ready to interact with the api.
    StatusChangeEvent
    This event is dispatched when a user's status changes.
    TypingEvent
    This event is dispatched if a user is typing.
    UserBanEvent
    This event is dispatched when a user is banned from a guild.
    UserJoinEvent
    This is dispatched when a user is added/joins a guild.
    UserLeaveEvent
    This event is dispatched when a guild member is removed/leaves from a guild
    UserPardonEvent
    This event is dispatched when a user is pardoned from a ban.
    UserRoleUpdateEvent
    This event is dispatched when a guild updates a user's roles.
    UserUpdateEvent
    This is dispatched whenever a user updates his/her info
    UserVoiceChannelJoinEvent
    This event is dispatched when a user connects to a voice channel.
    UserVoiceChannelLeaveEvent
    This event is dispatched when a user disconnects from a voice channel.
    UserVoiceChannelMoveEvent
    This event is dispatched when a user moves from one voice channel to another.
    VoiceChannelCreateEvent
    This event is dispatched when a voice channel is created.
    VoiceChannelDeleteEvent
    This event is dispatched when a voice channel is deleted.
    VoiceChannelUpdateEvent
    This event is dispatched when a voice channel is updated.
    VoiceDisconnectedEvent
    This event is dispatched when either the client loses connection to discord or is logged out.
    VoicePingEvent
    This event is dispatched when a voice heartbeat is received.
    VoiceUserSpeakingEvent
    This is dispatched when a user starts or stops speaking
    WebhookCreateEvent
    This event is dispatched whenever a webhook is created or discovered.
    WebhookDeleteEvent
    This event is dispatched whenever a webhook is deleted, or access to it is lost.
    WebhookUpdateEvent
    This event is dispatched whenever a webhook is updated.

    This enum represents the possible reasons for discord being disconnected.
